{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bf09554ed1","title":"建立空军已成党的道切任务","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2e0bb13d2b","index":0,"year":1947,"month":12,"day":5,"articleId":"bf09554ed1"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"205df89980","type":"paragraph","text":"建立空军已成党的道切任务口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"bf09554ed1"},{"id":"d0243466c8","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年12月5日）建立空军已经成了我党的迫切任务，你们对此有何计划[1]这是毛泽东在周恩来1947年12月5日为中共中央军委起草的给中共中央东北局电报上加写的一句话。周恩来的电报说：“你处关于建立空军的准备工作，如飞机终存的数量、种类，修理装制的能力，机件汽油的储各，空军人员的训练和数量，空军基地，航空站及工厂的准备以及可能发展的条件等等，统望电告。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"bf09554ed1"}],"page":{"id":"266d27ffc0","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"bf09554ed1","start":421,"end":421}}}},"__N_SSG":true}